    <string name="rules_text">
        <u><b>Goal:</b></u>\n
        The goal of the game is go to all the waypoints/checkpoints on the map, and answer
            the trivia questions at each of them.\n
        \n
        <u><b>Game rules:</b></u>\n
        1) To reach a waypoint, you need to be in a radius of 10m around it.\n
        2) If you fail to complete a waypoint, you need to go to another one before coming back.\n
        \n
        <u><b>Preparing a game:</b></u>\n
        \u2022 Create a game, and remember its name: each player will need to enter it
            (with exact upper/lower case).\n
        \u2022 The game is deleted after it has been played, or automatically after 30 days.\n
        \n
        <u><b>Watch companion app:</b></u>\n
        If you have a WearOS smart watch, you can install the companion app on it, and open the app.
            The watch app enables easier access to a compass while navigating to a specific waypoint !
